sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Customer
    participant V as Vercel API (/api/online-order)
    participant G as Google Apps Script
    participant S as Google Sheets

    C->>+V: POST /api/online-order (placeOrder)
    V->>+G: fetch(GAS_URL)
    G->>+S: appendRow(orderData)
    S-->>-G: Success
    G-->>-V: { success: true }
    V-->>-C: { ok: true, orderRef }

    Note right of V: Prone to failure under load due to\nGAS 30 concurrent execution limit.
